---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Men's Coaching Through Divorce: Rebuilding Your Life | Tom Jameson"
    description="Navigate the challenges of divorce with professional men's coaching support, learning to rebuild confidence and create a new path forward."
    canonical="https://tomcoaching.com/blog/mens-coaching-divorce"
>
    <div class="blog-post-container">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="breadcrumb">
                <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/blog">Blog</a> / Men's Coaching Through Divorce
            </nav>

            <article class="blog-post">
                <header class="post-header">
                    <div class="post-meta">
                        <span class="category">Relationships</span>
                        <span class="date">December 19, 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h1>Men's Coaching Through Divorce: Rebuilding Your Life</h1>
                    <p class="post-excerpt">Navigate the challenges of divorce with professional men's coaching support, learning to rebuild confidence and create a new path forward.</p>
                </header>

                <div class="post-content">
                    <p>Divorce represents one of life's most challenging transitions, and men's coaching provides essential support during this difficult period. Professional coaching helps men navigate the emotional, financial, and practical aspects of divorce while maintaining their dignity and focusing on personal growth.</p>

                    <p>Men often face unique challenges during divorce, including concerns about custody, financial stability, and rebuilding their identity as single men. Coaching provides a safe space to process emotions, develop coping strategies, and create actionable plans for moving forward with confidence and purpose.</p>

                    <p>Effective divorce coaching for men includes developing communication skills for co-parenting, managing stress and anxiety, rebuilding self-esteem, and creating new goals for the future. Coaches help clients identify their strengths, address limiting beliefs, and develop the resilience needed to thrive in their new circumstances.</p>

                    <p>Whether you're in the early stages of separation or adjusting to post-divorce life, men's coaching can provide the guidance and support you need to heal, grow, and create a fulfilling new chapter in your life.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="related-articles">
                    <h3>Related Articles</h3>
                    <div class="related-grid">
                        <a href="/blog/mens-family-coaching" class="related-card">
                            <h4>Men's Family Coaching: Strengthening Fatherhood and Relationships</h4>
                            <p>Strengthen your role as a father and family leader.</p>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/blog/mens-personal-coaching" class="related-card">
                            <h4>Men's Personal Coaching: Building Confidence and Self-Worth</h4>
                            <p>Transform your self-confidence and personal worth.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="post-cta">
                    <h3>Ready to Rebuild Your Life?</h3>
                    <p>Take the first step towards healing and creating a new future with professional coaching support.</p>
                    <a href="/#contact" class="btn">Book Your Consultation Today</a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        .blog-post-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .breadcrumb {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: #d0c39b;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .breadcrumb a:hover {
            color: #172a22;
        }

        .blog-post {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .post-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .post-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .category {
            background: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .date {
            color: #666;
        }

        .post-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .post-excerpt {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .post-content {
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .post-content p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .related-articles {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .related-articles h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .related-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .related-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .related-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .related-card h4 {
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .related-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .post-cta {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #172a22 0%, #1e3a2e 100%);
            color: #d0c39b;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .post-cta h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .post-cta p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #c4b082;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .blog-post {
                padding: 2rem;
                margin: 0 1rem;
            }
            
            .post-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .post-meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>

